amics, while the global mode of smaller amplitude is always unstable (theory\nconfirms this). However, advection can stabilize the mode of larger amplitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Dec 2014 16:18:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Jan 2015 11:04:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-30"}
