as in cooling condensations that form\ninside the contact discontinuity account for most of the Bubbles' \\gamma-ray\nemissivity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Dec 2014 20:40:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2015 03:30:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-30"}
