 looking at phase\ntransitions demystifies the emergence of order parameters and provides a unique\nnovel tool for studying exotic quantum phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Dec 2014 10:58:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2015 21:50:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2015 10:33:30 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2016 03:54:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-18"}
